   437→        created_at: 2026-03-10T05:08:54.776Z
   438→        author: "@claude"
   439→        content: >-
   440→          3 bugs fixed in session-discovery.ts:
   441→
   442→          1. SQLite connection leak: db.close() was not in try-finally — if prepare/all threw,
   443→          connection stayed open. Wrapped in try-finally with safe close.
   444→
   445→          2. Race condition: stat() was called before readFile(), so mtime/size could mismatch
   446→          content. Swapped order (read first, then stat). Added parse error counting with warning
   447→          for multi-line corruption (>1 failed line).
   448→
   449→          3. Legacy path encoding: Claude used two different encoding schemes (old: no leading dash,
   450→          spaces preserved; new: leading dash, spaces→dashes). Only new scheme was checked. Added
   451→          encodeProjectPathLegacy() and multi-dir scanning with deduplication by sessionId.
