   478→      - _ulid: 01KKB391FJ67DSH2HVC2TK06SN
   479→        created_at: 2026-03-10T05:24:52.338Z
   480→        author: "@claude"
   481→        content: >-
   482→          4 bugs fixed:
   483→
   484→          1. useDragAndDrop.ts: stale dropTarget position — handleProjectDrop and
   485→          handleCategoryHeaderDrop read dropTarget?.position from React state closure which could be
   486→          stale when drop fires (React may not have re-rendered since last dragOver). Added
   487→          dropTargetRef that's updated synchronously alongside state, so drop handlers always read
   488→          the latest position.
   489→
   490→          2. useSidebarHandlers.ts: rename Escape saves via blur — pressing Escape during inline
   491→          rename calls setEditingProject(null), React unmounts the input, browser fires blur with
   492→          the OLD handler that still has editingProject in closure, causing an unwanted save. Added
